how much this means to me?

11:25.728 --> 11:27.034
Okay, what do you want?

11:32.039 --> 11:34.258
Okay, I'll get you the pony.

11:34.345 --> 11:37.784
But, first, you have
to show me the stash.

11:39.524 --> 11:41.875
Fine. Pony first.

11:43.528 --> 11:45.139
Oh, Dewey.

11:45.226 --> 11:46.531
I need your help.

11:46.618 --> 11:48.011
