everyone's conversations.

11:50.187 --> 11:51.493
Do you have any
dirt on your mom?

11:51.580 --> 11:54.322
I need something
really big and awful.

11:54.409 --> 11:55.889
I did something bad,

11:55.976 --> 11:57.586
so I have to find something
that she did bad,

11:57.673 --> 11:59.022
then I can confess
what I did,

11:59.109 --> 12:00.807
and it won't seem
like such a big deal.

12:00.894 --> 12:02.460
