of your backpack?!

12:38.409 --> 12:40.107
-Yes, I do.
-I'm not interested!

12:40.194 --> 12:41.935
You are not finding
another job!

12:42.022 --> 12:43.197
Huh? No! I...

12:43.284 --> 12:44.851
You are not getting a job

12:44.938 --> 12:46.896
away from my constant
supervision, and that's it.

12:46.983 --> 12:48.245
I'm not going
to risk your future

12:48.332 --> 12:49.856
by giving you even
a second of freedom!

12:49.943 --> 12:51.596
This family has too much
invested in you.

12:52.859 --> 12:54.077
Oh, cheer up.

12:54.164 --> 12:55.949
Once I find
a proper wife for you,

12:56.036 --> 12:57.777
you'll have
your precious space.

12:59.256 --> 13:02.042
